<div class="publication-details-hiddenbox"><p class="publication-details"><strong>Keywords: </strong><span xml:lang="en">NorNet, NorNet Core, Testbed, Multi-Homing, Multi-Path Transport, Tutorial</span></p><p class="publication-details"><strong>Abstract: </strong><span xml:lang="en">This tutorial – presented for students at the College of Information Science and Technology&nbsp;(CIST) at Hainan University – provides an introduction on how to get access to the NorNet Core testbed as well as how to run experiments in the testbed.</span></p><p class="publication-details" style="text-align: left;"><strong>URL:&nbsp;</strong><a type="application/pdf" href="https://web-backend.simula.no/sites/default/files/publications/files/haikou2016-hainanuniversity-tutorial_0.pdf">https://web-backend.simula.no/sites/default/files/publications/files/haikou2016-hainanuniversity-tutorial_0.pdf</a></p><p class="publication-details"><strong>MD5: </strong> 65d8e35c633a55315b7f72a764d7d970</p></div>
