<div class="publication-details-hiddenbox"><p class="publication-details"><strong>Keywords: </strong><span xml:lang="en">NorNet, NorNet Core, Testbed, Multi-Homing, Multi-Path Transport, Tutorial</span></p><p class="publication-details"><strong>Abstract: </strong><span xml:lang="en">This tutorial provides an introduction on how to get access to the NorNet Core testbed as well as how to run experiments in the testbed.</span></p><p class="publication-details" style="text-align: left;"><strong>URL:&nbsp;</strong><a type="application/pdf" href="https://web-backend.simula.no/sites/default/files/publications/Simula.simula.2938.pdf">https://web-backend.simula.no/sites/default/files/publications/Simula.simula.2938.pdf</a></p><p class="publication-details"><strong>MD5: </strong> 9711b4f32dd9a2c4946aa4aeceeac31c</p></div>
