<div class="publication-details-hiddenbox"><p class="publication-details"><strong>Keywords: </strong><span xml:lang="en">NorNet, Testbed, Multi-Homing, Setup, Research</span></p><p class="publication-details"><strong>Abstract: </strong><span xml:lang="en">This talk gives an overview of the NorNet project, the new Internet testbed for multi-homed systems, and its research objectives.</span></p><p class="publication-details" style="text-align: left;"><strong>URL:&nbsp;</strong><a type="application/pdf" href="https://web-backend.simula.no/sites/default/files/publications/Simula.simula.1968.pdf">https://web-backend.simula.no/sites/default/files/publications/Simula.simula.1968.pdf</a></p><p class="publication-details"><strong>MD5: </strong> 3855ef4890e243dd180cc9f8abd745f6</p></div>
